<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SW Certificates</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003366 50%, #00aaff 50%);
            color: white;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2em 1em;
            background-color: #003366;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .container {
            margin: 2em auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .certificate {
            background: white;
            color: #003366;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .certificate:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .certificate h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1em;
        }
        .certificate p {
            margin: 0.5em 1em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .certificate strong {
            color: #00aaff;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin: 1em;
        }
        .enroll-btn {
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #00aaff;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            width: 150px;
        }
        .enroll-btn:hover {
            background-color: #003366;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>SW Certificates</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="certificate">
            <h2>Certified ScrumMaster (CSM)</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> This certification demonstrates your understanding of Scrum principles and practices. It prepares you to be an effective Scrum Master, guiding teams through the Scrum framework to deliver high-quality projects in an Agile environment.</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 2-3 days of training (required by Scrum Alliance) followed by self-study.</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> The cost of training typically ranges from $1000 to $2000, which includes the exam fee.</p>
            <p><strong>How to Enroll:</strong> Visit the official Scrum Alliance CSM page, choose a training provider, and complete the required course. Once completed, you can take the exam through the Scrum Alliance website.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://www.scrumalliance.org/get-certified/scrum-master-track/certified-scrummaster" class="enroll-btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="certificate">
            <h2>Microsoft Certified: DevOps Engineer Expert</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> This certification validates your ability to combine people, process, and technologies to deliver high-quality products and services in DevOps environments. It includes managing source control, continuous integration, continuous delivery, and monitoring in cloud and hybrid environments.</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 2-4 months of study, depending on your prior experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Exam fee is $165 USD.</p>
            <p><strong>How to Enroll:</strong> Visit the official Microsoft Certification page, create an account, and schedule your exam. Preparation materials and practice tests are available on the same platform.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/certifications/devops-engineer/" class="enroll-btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="certificate">
            <h2>AWS Certified DevOps Engineer - Professional</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> This certification demonstrates your expertise in provisioning, operating, and managing distributed application systems on AWS. It focuses on implementing DevOps best practices for monitoring, security, and automation of the software development lifecycle.</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Approximately 3-6 months of study, depending on your prior experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Exam fee is $300 USD.</p>
            <p><strong>How to Enroll:</strong> Visit the official AWS Certification page, create an account, and schedule your exam. You can find preparation materials and practice exams on the same platform.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/certification/certified-devops-engineer-professional/" class="enroll-btn">Enroll Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>